took her hand and squeezed it with a faint smile mrs barry 
patted his hand comfortingly and whispered to him 
following her husbands statement mrs barry announced that she 
and their son christopher 9 would stand by him 
for our family this is just the beginning she said and 
we will be with you every step of the way 
