negotiations in geneva will continue in their absence 
burt said he hoped for progress in moscow on the most difficult 
remaining start issues the permitted range of airlaunched cruise 
missiles how to count them and how what to do about bombers that 
carry such missiles equipped with conventional rather than nuclear 
warheads 
