consumer product safety commission staff 
members say adult sleepwear should be labeled according to its 
degree of flammability to help prevent fire deaths among the 
elderly manufacturers argue that a simple warning would do the job 
the commission will soon consider staff and industry 
recommendations for adult sleepwear labeling after postponing a 
